title: Sex Madness (1938) PSA Quasi-Documentary, Propaganda Drama

sources.title: Sex Madness (1938) PSA Quasi-Documentary, Propaganda Drama
sources.description:
This exploitation film belongs to the social guidance genre of quasi-documentary narratives, which exhort young adults to follow particular moral and social prescriptions related to sexuality and drug use.

Director: Dwain Esper
Writers: Joseph Seiden, Vincent Valentini 
Stars  Vivian McGill, Rose Tapley, Al Rigali
